CodScop

Code analyzing tool for computing sloc and other metrics of code.


DESCRIPTION
If you want to know how many lines of code your project have or some other 
metrics of your project then CodScop can help you.

FEATURES
- Packages, classes, functions and inner classes are counted.
- XML output (planned).
- 100% Pure Scala.
- Free software (GNU GPL).

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
Java JDK >= 1.6

LICENSE
GNU LGPL 3.0

